description:
Their music blends composition and improvisation, acoustic and electronic
sounds, and varied time signatures, offering a fresh approach to jazz while
honoring its traditions. In October 2024, MoonMot will embark on an India tour
to showcase their new album, "Frugal."

address.streetAddress: Windmills IMAGINE, No. 78, ITPL Main Road, EPIP Zone,Bangalore

name: MoonMot

performer.description: MoonMot is a contemporary jazz quintet featuring musicians from Switzerland and Great Britain. The lineup includes London saxophonist Dee Byrne, Swiss trombonist Simon Petermann, keyboardist Oli Kuster from Bern, Scottish bassist Seth Bennett, and Manchester drummer Johnny Hunter.
performer.name: MoonMot
